REALM english_config

LET function(s) BE s OR z OR es OR ez OR ies OR iez OR y>ies OR y>iez OR ing OR ings OR ed OR er OR ers OR y OR ys
LET function(vulnerable) BE kid OR kids OR child OR children OR kiddie OR kiddies OR baby OR babies OR babys OR minor OR minors OR son OR sons OR daughter OR daughters OR boy OR boys OR girl OR girls OR nephew OR niece OR toddler OR infant
LET function(declarative) BE a OR the OR my OR your OR his OR her OR their OR that OR some
LET function(accuse) BE you are OR you're OR youre OR ur a OR your a OR im a OR i'm a OR am a OR is a OR hes a OR he's a OR shes a OR she's a OR fuckin OR looking for OR are you a OR u a OR such a OR stop being OR stop acting like OR act like a OR dont be a OR don't be a
LET function(sexverb) BE wore OR wear OR wearing OR worn OR use OR used OR using OR put OR putting OR stole OR stolen OR bought OR buy OR buying OR need OR needed OR want OR wanted OR bring OR brought OR forgot OR got OR grab OR grabbed OR slip OR slipped OR roll OR rolled OR without
LET function(selfharmverb) BE neck OR hang OR off OR unalive OR cut OR slice OR shoot OR shot OR slit
LET function(genderword) BE female OR girl OR woman OR womens OR male OR mens OR guy OR guys OR men OR man
LET function(article) BE a OR an OR the OR on OR no OR my OR your OR his OR her OR some
LET function(frenchstuff) (WHOLE) BE franger OR frenchie OR jizzbag OR french LAZY letter OR cock LAZY sock OR cum LAZY catcher OR santa LAZY sock OR jimmy LAZY hat
LET function(seeking) BE watch OR have OR havin OR got OR gotta OR need OR gimme OR give me OR send OR dm OR dms OR hit me up OR look OR searching OR search for OR where to find OR where can i OR wya for OR want OR wanna OR who has OR who got OR who selling OR anyone OR can i get OR let me see OR lemme see OR share OR trade OR sell OR buy OR purchase OR download OR leak OR drop the OR drop some OR droppin OR collection OR pic OR video OR vid OR content OR link OR menu OR catalog OR pack OR mega OR dropbox OR drop box OR onedrive OR gdrive OR google drive OR telegram OR discord OR nz OR db OR folder OR archive OR gb OR gigabyte OR mb OR megabyte OR tb OR terabyte
LET function(subject) BE i OR im OR i'm OR me OR she OR shes OR she's OR he OR hes OR he's OR they OR we OR you OR ur OR you're OR youre OR my OR his OR her OR their OR she is OR he is OR they are OR i am OR we are OR you are OR who
LET function(desire) BE want OR wanna OR wants OR wanting OR need OR needs OR needing OR have OR having OR has OR got OR gotta OR gimme OR give me OR send OR dm OR dms OR hit me up OR look OR looking for OR search for OR searching OR searching for OR where to find OR where can i find OR wya for OR who has OR who got OR who selling OR anyone selling OR can i get OR get OR get me OR gonna get OR gonna OR gonna have OR gonna want OR gonna need OR i want to OR i need to OR i wanna OR i have to OR want to OR need to OR have to OR desire to OR dream to OR please OR pls OR plz OR plese OR pse OR ps OR pplz OR ppls
LET function(quantifier) BE NONE OR some OR any OR a OR an OR the OR that OR those OR this OR these OR em OR some of the OR some of these OR some of those OR some of this OR some of it

